name: LitRadio
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lit radio
des:
To open the player say: Alexa, play Lit Radio. 

Next station: Alexa skip / Alexa next. 

Previous station: Alexa back / Alexa previous. 

To play the station: Alexa stop / Alexa pause - listen to the message, say the number of the station. For example: Alexa two (it will play Start Fm radio station)

To exit the player: Alexa cancel.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
